I shall get the fame too.

716
01:01:41,800 --> 01:01:43,880
Good heavens, what's this?

717
01:01:45,240 --> 01:01:47,440
It's nothing.
Just some local urchins.

718
01:02:02,080 --> 01:02:05,840
