like a restless sea?

729
01:02:42,320 --> 01:02:43,840
How poetic.

730
01:02:44,040 --> 01:02:45,840
Yes, it was rather, wasn't it?

731
01:02:46,920 --> 01:02:51,840
More at home here than in Vienna
in all your glittering salons. . .

732
01:02:52,040 --> 01:02:56,240
